data.description: Enjoy the peace & privacy of having no neighbors behind your new privacy fenced backyard! Nestled on .26/acre lot in the backside of the desirable & established subdivision of ZACHARY ESTATES is this beautiful, thoughtful, open & split floorplan home that was built in 2018 & features:  3BR/2BA/1,590SF/2-car garage, underground utilities, irrigation system, gutters around all sides, a Generac whole house generator, water softner, water filtration system, GAS items- stove/oven, furnace, water heater, & dryer option, blinds on all windows, & a partially enclosed FL room! 2023 UPDATES include: freshly painted interior walls, granite countertops in kitchen & bathrooms, waterproof laminate flooring in the entry, dining area, kitchen, & bathrooms, new dishwasher, lighting fixtures, & more! There's just SO MUCH to love and enjoy inside & outside of this 2018 built home that feels like it's brand new! You'll love all the GAS items that help keep the electric bill low: water heater, furnace, stove/oven, & there is a dryer option! The dishwasher was just replaced - 2023. Spend time reading & napping on your custom built daybed located in your screened-in Florida room that has the option to be partially enclosed with easy detatchable vinyl windows! There is a whole yard sprinkler system that uses city water to irrigate. All kitchen appliances, garage fridge, murphy bed with matching shelving in front guest room, custom day bed in FL room, & outdoor sun shade covering will convey. Other wonderful features about this home include the transferable yearly termite contract with Anchor Pest Control that was just renewed in July ($300) and the transferable yearly hvac contract with Peadon Air that was just renewed in August ($109). Since Sellers purchased this home in June of 2022, they have updated the kitchen & bathrooms with granite countertops, changed flooring in entry, kitchen, bathrooms, & laundry to waterproof plank laminate, changed light fixtures throughout, replaced both bathroom mirrors, painted all interior rooms, replaced the dishwasher, & added privacy fencing in the backyard. Since the property is located in Flood Zone X, flood insurance is NOT required! The HOA for Zachary Estates is only $185 per year! This beautiful and very recently updated home, along with the quaint subdivision of Zachary Estates, are a must see to love, desire, and truly appreciate!
